#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.20:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Sīhanādavagga"
msgstr "2. The Lion’s Roar"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Velāmasutta"
msgstr "20. About Velāma"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an9.20:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.393"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:2.1"
msgid "“Api nu te, gahapati, kule dānaṃ dīyatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Householder, I wonder whether your family gives gifts?”"

msgctxt "an9.20:2.2"
msgid "“Dīyati me, bhante, kule dānaṃ;"
msgstr "“It does, sir."

msgctxt "an9.20:2.3"
msgid "tañca kho lūkhaṃ kaṇājakaṃ biḷaṅgadutiyan”ti."
msgstr "But only coarse gruel with pickles.”"

#. VAR: Lūkhañcepi → lūkhaṃ vāpi (s1-3) | lūkhañcāpi (mr)
msgctxt "an9.20:2.4"
msgid "“Lūkhañcepi, gahapati, dānaṃ deti paṇītaṃ vā;"
msgstr "“Householder, someone might give a gift that’s either coarse or fine."

#. VAR: acittīkatvā → acittikatvā (bj, pts1) | apacittiṃ katvā (s1-3) | acittiṃ katvā (mr)
#. VAR: apaviddhaṃ → apaviṭṭhaṃ (s1, s2)
msgctxt "an9.20:2.5"
msgid ""
"tañca asakkaccaṃ deti, acittīkatvā deti, asahatthā deti, apaviddhaṃ deti, "
"anāgamanadiṭṭhiko deti."
msgstr ""
"But they give it carelessly, thoughtlessly, not with their own hand. They "
"give the dregs, and they give without consideration for consequences."

msgctxt "an9.20:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yattha yattha tassa tassa dānassa vipāko nibbattati, na uḷārāya "
"bhattabhogāya cittaṃ namati, na uḷārāya vatthabhogāya cittaṃ namati, na "
"uḷārāya yānabhogāya cittaṃ namati, na uḷāresu pañcasu kāmaguṇesu bhogāya "
"cittaṃ namati."
msgstr ""
"Then wherever the result of any such gift manifests, their mind doesn’t tend "
"to enjoy nice food, clothes, vehicles, or the five refined kinds of sensual "
"stimulation."

msgctxt "an9.20:2.7"
msgid ""
"Yepissa te honti puttāti vā dārāti vā dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, "
"tepi na sussūsanti na sotaṃ odahanti na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti."
msgstr ""
"And their children, wives, bondservants, employees, and workers don’t want "
"to listen to them. They don’t pay attention or try to understand."

msgctxt "an9.20:2.8"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

#. VAR: Evañhetaṃ → evañcetaṃ (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: asakkaccaṃ katānaṃ → asakkaccakatānaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an9.20:2.9"
msgid "Evañhetaṃ, gahapati, hoti asakkaccaṃ katānaṃ kammānaṃ vipāko."
msgstr "Because that is the result of deeds done carelessly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:3.1"
msgid "Lūkhañcepi, gahapati, dānaṃ deti paṇītaṃ vā;"
msgstr "Someone might give a gift that’s either coarse or fine."

msgctxt "an9.20:3.2"
msgid ""
"tañca sakkaccaṃ deti, cittīkatvā deti, sahatthā deti, anapaviddhaṃ deti, "
"āgamanadiṭṭhiko deti."
msgstr ""
"And they give it carefully, thoughtfully, with their own hand. They don’t "
"give the dregs, and they give with consideration for consequences."

msgctxt "an9.20:3.3"
msgid ""
"Yattha yattha tassa tassa dānassa vipāko nibbattati, uḷārāya bhattabhogāya "
"cittaṃ namati, uḷārāya vatthabhogāya cittaṃ namati, uḷārāya yānabhogāya "
"cittaṃ namati, uḷāresu pañcasu kāmaguṇesu bhogāya cittaṃ namati."
msgstr ""
"Then wherever the result of any such gift manifests, their mind tends to "
"enjoy nice food, clothes, vehicles, or the five refined kinds of sensual "
"stimulation."

msgctxt "an9.20:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yepissa te honti puttāti vā dārāti vā dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, "
"tepi sussūsanti sotaṃ odahanti aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti."
msgstr ""
"And their children, wives, bondservants, employees, and workers want to "
"listen. They pay attention and try to understand."

msgctxt "an9.20:3.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an9.20:3.6"
msgid "Evañhetaṃ, gahapati, hoti sakkaccaṃ katānaṃ kammānaṃ vipāko."
msgstr "Because that is the result of deeds done carefully."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.394"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:4.1"
msgid "Bhūtapubbaṃ, gahapati, velāmo nāma brāhmaṇo ahosi."
msgstr "Once upon a time, householder, there was a brahmin named Velāma."

msgctxt "an9.20:4.2"
msgid "So evarūpaṃ dānaṃ adāsi mahādānaṃ."
msgstr "He gave the following gift, a great offering."

#. VAR: hemajālappaṭicchannāni → hemajālasañchannāni (bj, pts1) | hemajālapaṭicchannāni (s1-3)
#. VAR: āmuttamaṇikuṇḍalāyo → āmukkamaṇikuṇḍalāyo (bj)
#. VAR: vissandanti → vissandati (si, pts1) | visandanti (s1-3)
msgctxt "an9.20:4.3"
msgid ""
"Caturāsīti suvaṇṇapātisahassāni adāsi rūpiyapūrāni, caturāsīti "
"rūpiyapātisahassāni adāsi suvaṇṇapūrāni, caturāsīti kaṃsapātisahassāni adāsi "
"hiraññapūrāni, caturāsīti hatthisahassāni adāsi sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni "
"sovaṇṇadhajāni hemajālappaṭicchannāni, caturāsīti rathasahassāni adāsi "
"sīhacammaparivārāni byagghacammaparivārāni dīpicammaparivārāni "
"paṇḍukambalaparivārāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni "
"hemajālappaṭicchannāni, caturāsīti dhenusahassāni adāsi dukūlasandhanāni "
"kaṃsūpadhāraṇāni, caturāsīti kaññāsahassāni adāsi āmuttamaṇikuṇḍalāyo, "
"caturāsīti pallaṅkasahassāni adāsi gonakatthatāni paṭikatthatāni "
"paṭalikatthatāni kadalimigapavarapaccattharaṇāni sauttaracchadāni "
"ubhatolohitakūpadhānāni, caturāsīti vatthakoṭisahassāni adāsi "
"khomasukhumānaṃ koseyyasukhumānaṃ kambalasukhumānaṃ kappāsikasukhumānaṃ, ko "
"pana vādo annassa pānassa khajjassa bhojjassa leyyassa peyyassa, najjo maññe "
"vissandanti."
msgstr ""
"84,000 gold bowls filled with silver. 84,000 silver bowls filled with gold. "
"84,000 bronze bowls filled with gold coins. 84,000 elephants with gold "
"adornments and banners, covered with gold netting. 84,000 chariots "
"upholstered with the hide of lions, tigers, and leopards, and cream rugs, "
"with gold adornments and banners, covered with gold netting. 84,000 milk "
"cows with silken reins and bronze pails. 84,000 maidens bedecked with jewels "
"and earrings. 84,000 couches spread with woolen covers—shag-piled, pure "
"white, or embroidered with flowers—and spread with a fine deer hide, with "
"canopies above and red pillows at both ends. 8,400,000,000 fine cloths of "
"linen, silk, wool, and cotton. And who can say how much food, drink, snacks, "
"meals, refreshments, and beverages? It seemed to flow like a river."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:5.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, gahapati, evamassa:"
msgstr "Householder, you might think:"

#. VAR: so → yo (?)
msgctxt "an9.20:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘añño nūna tena samayena velāmo brāhmaṇo ahosi, so taṃ dānaṃ adāsi "
"mahādānan’ti."
msgstr "‘Surely the brahmin Velāma must have been someone else at that time?’"

msgctxt "an9.20:5.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, gahapati, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "an9.20:5.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ tena samayena velāmo brāhmaṇo ahosiṃ."
msgstr "I myself was the brahmin Velāma at that time."

msgctxt "an9.20:5.5"
msgid "Ahaṃ taṃ dānaṃ adāsiṃ mahādānaṃ."
msgstr "I gave that gift, a great offering."

msgctxt "an9.20:5.6"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ kho pana, gahapati, dāne na koci dakkhiṇeyyo ahosi, na taṃ koci "
"dakkhiṇaṃ visodheti."
msgstr ""
"But at that event there was no-one worthy of a teacher’s offering, and no-"
"one to purify the teacher’s offering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, gahapati, velāmo brāhmaṇo dānaṃ adāsi mahādānaṃ, yo cekaṃ "
"diṭṭhisampannaṃ bhojeyya, idaṃ tato mahapphalataraṃ."
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one person accomplished in view than that "
"great offering of Velāma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: () → (yañca gahapati velāmo brāhmaṇo dānaṃ adāsi mahādānaṃ) (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an9.20:7.1"
msgid ""
"() Yo ca sataṃ diṭṭhisampannānaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ sakadāgāmiṃ bhojeyya, "
"idaṃ tato mahapphalataraṃ."
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one once-returner than a hundred persons "
"accomplished in view."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.395"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: () → (yañca gahapati velāmo brāhmaṇo dānaṃ adāsi mahādānaṃ) (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an9.20:8.1"
msgid ""
"() Yo ca sataṃ sakadāgāmīnaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ anāgāmiṃ bhojeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one non-returner than a hundred once-"
"returners."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.2"
msgid "yo ca sataṃ anāgāmīnaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ arahantaṃ bhojeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one perfected one than a hundred non-"
"returners."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.3"
msgid ""
"yo ca sataṃ arahantānaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ paccekabuddhaṃ bhojeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one Buddha awakened for themselves than a "
"hundred perfected ones."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.4"
msgid ""
"yo ca sataṃ paccekabuddhānaṃ bhojeyya, yo ca tathāgataṃ arahantaṃ "
"sammāsambuddhaṃ bhojeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed one Realized One, a perfected one, a fully "
"awakened Buddha than a hundred Buddhas awakened for themselves."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.5"
msgid "yo ca buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṃghaṃ bhojeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to feed the mendicant Saṅgha headed by the Buddha "
"than to feed one Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.6"
msgid "yo ca cātuddisaṃ saṃghaṃ uddissa vihāraṃ kārāpeyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to build a dwelling especially for the Saṅgha of "
"the four quarters than to feed the mendicant Saṅgha headed by the Buddha."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.7"
msgid ""
"yo ca pasannacitto buddhañca dhammañca saṃghañca saraṇaṃ gaccheyya … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to go for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and "
"the Saṅgha with a confident heart than to build a dwelling for the Saṅgha of "
"the four quarters."

msgctxt "an9.20:8.8"
msgid "yo ca pasannacitto sikkhāpadāni samādiyeyya—"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to undertake the training rules—not to kill living "
"creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or take alcoholic drinks "
"that cause negligence—than to go for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and "
"the Saṅgha with a confident heart."

#. VAR: gandhohanamattampi → gandhūhanamattampi (bj) | gaddūhanamattampi (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: () → (yo ca accharāsaṅghātamattampi aniccasaññaṃ bhāveyya) (mr)
msgctxt "an9.20:8.9"
msgid ""
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiṃ, adinnādānā veramaṇiṃ, kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇiṃ, "
"musāvādā veramaṇiṃ, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiṃ, yo ca antamaso "
"gandhohanamattampi mettacittaṃ bhāveyya, () idaṃ tato mahapphalataraṃ."
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful to develop a heart of love—even just as long as it "
"takes to pull a cow’s udder—than to undertake the training rules."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.396"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:9.1"
msgid ""
"Yañca, gahapati, velāmo brāhmaṇo dānaṃ adāsi mahādānaṃ, yo cekaṃ "
"diṭṭhisampannaṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""
"It would be more fruitful develop the perception of impermanence—even for as "
"long as a finger snap—than to do all of these things, including developing a "
"heart of love for as long as it takes to pull a cow’s udder.”"

msgctxt "an9.20:9.2"
msgid "yo ca sataṃ diṭṭhisampannānaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ sakadāgāmiṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.3"
msgid "yo ca sataṃ sakadāgāmīnaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ anāgāmiṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.4"
msgid "yo ca sataṃ anāgāmīnaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ arahantaṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.5"
msgid "yo ca sataṃ arahantānaṃ bhojeyya, yo cekaṃ paccekabuddhaṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.6"
msgid ""
"yo ca sataṃ paccekabuddhānaṃ bhojeyya, yo ca tathāgataṃ arahantaṃ "
"sammāsambuddhaṃ bhojeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.7"
msgid ""
"yo ca buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ bhojeyya, yo ca cātuddisaṃ saṅghaṃ "
"uddissa vihāraṃ kārāpeyya …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.8"
msgid ""
"yo ca pasannacitto buddhañca dhammañca saṅghañca saraṇaṃ gaccheyya, yo ca "
"pasannacitto sikkhāpadāni samādiyeyya—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.20:9.9"
msgid ""
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiṃ … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiṃ, yo ca "
"antamaso gandhohanamattampi mettacittaṃ bhāveyya, yo ca "
"accharāsaṅghātamattampi aniccasaññaṃ bhāveyya, idaṃ tato mahapphalataran”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.20:9.10"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.20:9.11"
msgid "Sīhanādavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an9.20:10.1"
msgid "Nādo saupādiseso ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.20:10.2"
msgid "koṭṭhikena samiddhinā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.20:10.3"
msgid "Gaṇḍasaññā kulaṃ mettā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.20:10.4"
msgid "devatā velāmena cāti."
msgstr ""
